{"tid":1505762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"設立俾黑狗既死線","createTime":"2019-08-25T15:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T15:44:10.000Z","uid":41102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d945d68bd1c1f3b35d7f4018b8713a6fdeb68f9","tid":1505762,"uid":41102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"係社運上要成功就必需要靠和勇合力<br />\n和理非遊行&gt;set死線&gt;勇武升級<br />\n不停loop至成功爭取訴求<br />\n但係事實係我地已經係呢場運動損失咗5位手足、800個兄弟可能要付上佢地既青春、3隻眼仲有更多更多<br />\n我地既損失歸咎於無能既政府既時候，同時有好大既責任係班濫權濫捕無人性既狗<br />\n有見及此，我覺得我地同時都要set條底線俾班狗<br />\n例如 1.若然再係示威期間，狗再爆市民1隻眼<br />\n我地就除左星期6日示威外，平日一至五會係狗仔/狗女既校外接放學，同佢班同學做放映會，介紹下該名狗仔老豆做過咩，我地要點對佢<br />\n例如2. 若濫捕人數多過900人，我地就係狗竇外為佢地做食物安全檢測，不量生熟食物為其安全着想都要驗一驗否則不得內進<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37adf612406719d97574086356fe486606cb7b56","tid":1505762,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f3997a0819098189c8d17209e4adbf4d623259e","tid":1505762,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><